To construct visually compelling charts with [/benchmark_results.csv](file:///c:/Users/Dhananjay%20Singh/Desktop/BTP_SEM8_MEDA/benchmark_results.csv):
1. **Cross Contamination Scatter Plot:** Scatterplot of **Mixes (`m`)** on the X-axis vs **Max Dilution (`maxL`)** on the Y-Axis. This vividly proves LARP and ILP occupy the top-left (the best of both worlds), while BS occupies the bottom-left and RMA the top-right.
